data.description: Enjoy townhome living at its finest. Sought after Timber Trails end unit with oversized 2 1/2 car garage. This impressive family home sits on a quiet street, just a short 2 block walk from Timber Trails neighborhood park.  A beautifully tiled entry way invites you into the heart of the home. Enjoy a sunny spacious living room with plenty of windows & oversized two-story cathedral ceiling.  Open floor space includes a bright natural kitchen with prep island, pantry closet and table area.   Additional features include a large family room loft area, 2 sizeable bedrooms, two full & one-half bathrooms, convenient 2nd floor laundry room, exclusive upgraded primary bathroom and a private main floor office with glass pane French doors.       Bring your best offer this one is sure to move fast!
